<name>Text Width</name>
<group>draw</group>
<synopsis>Calculates the width in pixels of some text</synopsis>
<syntax><i>width</i> = Text Width (<i>string</i>)</syntax>
<desc>
Calculates the width in pixels that the given string will occupy if drawn on the current canvas with the current font settings by the @@Draw Text@@ command.

See also:
	The @@Text Height@@, @@Text Descent@@ and @@Draw Text@@ functions.
</desc>
